{"ID":"20220906203702-09m66ac","Spec":"1","Type":"NodeDocument","Properties":{"id":"20220906203702-09m66ac","title":"d-2-redis","type":"doc","updated":"20220906203702"},"Children":[{"ID":"20220906203703-811e6k5","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":2,"Properties":{"id":"20220906203703-811e6k5","updated":"20220906203703"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeHeadingC8hMarker","Data":"## ","Properties":{"id":""}},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"4.3 Redis","Properties":{"id":""}}]},{"ID":"20220906203704-ta0pxmq","Type":"NodeBlockquote","Properties":{"id":"20220906203704-ta0pxmq","updated":"20220906203704"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeBlockquoteMarker","Data":"\u003e ","Properties":{"id":""}},{"ID":"20220906203705-8ogwoi9","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20220906203705-8ogwoi9","updated":"20220906203705"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","Properties":{"id":""},"TextMarkType":"a","TextMarkAHref":"https://javaguide.cn/","TextMarkTextContent":"JavaGuide"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":" ：「Java学习+面试指南」一份涵盖大部分 Java 程序员所需要掌握的核心知识。准备 Java 面试，首选 JavaGuide！","Properties":{"id":""}}]}]},{"ID":"20220906203706-9hppif6","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":3,"Properties":{"id":"20220906203706-9hppif6","updated":"20220906203706"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeHeadingC8hMarker","Data":"### ","Properties":{"id":""}},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"Redis 基础","Properties":{"id":""}}]},{"ID":"20220906203707-c99vh43","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":4,"Properties":{"id":"20220906203707-c99vh43","updated":"20220906203707"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeHeadingC8hMarker","Data":"#### ","Properties":{"id":""}},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"简单介绍一下 Redis!","Properties":{"id":""}}]},{"ID":"20220906203708-lguj9hp","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20220906203708-lguj9hp","updated":"20220906203708"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"简单来说 ","Properties":{"id":""}},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","Properties":{"id":""},"TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"Redis 就是一个使用 C 语言开发的数据库"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"，不过与传统数据库不同的是 ","Properties":{"id":""}},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","Properties":{"id":""},"TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"Redis 的数据是存在内存中的"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":" ，也就是它是内存数据库，所以读写速度非常快，因此 Redis 被广泛应用于缓存方向。","Properties":{"id":""}}]},{"ID":"20220906203709-cm52nk5","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20220906203709-cm52nk5","updated":"20220906203709"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"另外，Redis 除了做缓存之外，也经常用来做分布式锁，甚至是消息队列。","Properties":{"id":""}}]},{"ID":"20220906203710-08n3tx5","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20220906203710-08n3tx5","updated":"20220906203710"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"Redis 提供了多种数据类型来支持不同的业务场景。Redis 还支持事务 、持久化、Lua 脚本、多种集群方案。","Properties":{"id":""}}]},{"ID":"20220906203711-es00kyf","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20220906203711-es00kyf","updated":"20220906203711"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"你可以自己本机安装 Redis 或者通过 Redis 官网提供的","Properties":{"id":""}},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","Properties":{"id":""},"TextMarkType":"a","TextMarkAHref":"https://try.redis.io/","TextMarkTextContent":"在线 Redis 环境"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"来实际体验 Redis。","Properties":{"id":""}}]},{"ID":"20220906203712-vu797i4","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20220906203712-vu797i4","updated":"20220906203712"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeImage","Properties":{"id":""},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeBang","Data":"!","Properties":{"id":""}},{"Type":"NodeOpenBracket","Data":"[","Properties":{"id":""}},{"Type":"NodeLinkText","Data":"try-redis","Properties":{"id":""}},{"Type":"NodeCloseBracket","Data":"]","Properties":{"id":""}},{"Type":"NodeOpenParen","Data":"(","Properties":{"id":""}},{"Type":"NodeLinkDest","Data":"https://guide-blog-images.oss-cn-shenzhen.aliyuncs.com/github/javaguide/database/redis/try.redis.io.png","Properties":{"id":""}},{"Type":"NodeCloseParen","Data":")","Properties":{"id":""}}]}]},{"ID":"20220906203713-47j8c5j","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":4,"Properties":{"id":"20220906203713-47j8c5j","updated":"20220906203713"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeHeadingC8hMarker","Data":"#### ","Properties":{"id":""}},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"分布式缓存常见的技术选型方案有哪些？","Properties":{"id":""}}]},{"ID":"20220906203714-845iy39","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20220906203714-845iy39","updated":"20220906203714"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"分布式缓存的话，使用的比较多的主要是 ","Properties":{"id":""}},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","Properties":{"id":""},"TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"Memcached"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":" 和 ","Properties":{"id":""}},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","Properties":{"id":""},"TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"Redis"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"。不过，现在基本没有看过还有项目使用 ","Properties":{"id":""}},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","Properties":{"id":""},"TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"Memcached"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":" 来做缓存，都是直接用 ","Properties":{"id":""}},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","Properties":{"id":""},"TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"Redis"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"。","Properties":{"id":""}}]},{"ID":"20220906203715-qocnshg","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20220906203715-qocnshg","updated":"20220906203715"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"Memcached 是分布式缓存最开始兴起的那会，比较常用的。后来，随着 Redis 的发展，大家慢慢都转而使用更加强大的 Redis 了。","Properties":{"id":""}}]},{"ID":"20220906203716-438bjce","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20220906203716-438bjce","updated":"20220906203716"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"分布式缓存主要解决的是单机缓存的容量受服务器限制并且无法保存通用信息的问题。因为，本地缓存只在当前服务里有效，比如如果你部署了两个相同的服务，他们两者之间的缓存数据是无法共同的。","Properties":{"id":""}}]},{"ID":"20220906203717-6e2xp3j","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":4,"Properties":{"id":"20220906203717-6e2xp3j","updated":"20220906203717"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeHeadingC8hMarker","Data":"#### ","Properties":{"id":""}},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"说一下 Redis 和 Memcached 的区别和共同点","Properties":{"id":""}}]},{"ID":"20220906203718-qb8ro9z","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20220906203718-qb8ro9z","updated":"20220906203718"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"现在公司一般都是用 Redis 来实现缓存，而且 Redis 自身也越来越强大了！不过，了解 Redis 和 Memcached 的区别和共同点，有助于我们在做相应的技术选型的时候，能够做到有理有据！","Properties":{"id":""}}]},{"ID":"20220906203719-cp25xk0","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20220906203719-cp25xk0","updated":"20220906203719"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","Properties":{"id":""},"TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"共同点"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":" ：","Properties":{"id":""}}]},{"ID":"20220906203720-j1hgxne","Type":"NodeList","ListData":{"Typ":1,"Tight":true,"Start":1,"Delimiter":46,"Padding":3,"Marker":"MQ==","Num":1},"Properties":{"id":"20220906203720-j1hgxne","updated":"20220906203720"},"Children":[{"ID":"20220906203721-q0s3b1v","Type":"NodeListItem","Data":"1","ListData":{"Typ":1,"Tight":true,"Start":1,"Delimiter":46,"Padding":3,"Marker":"MQ==","Num":1},"Properties":{"id":"20220906203721-q0s3b1v","updated":"20220906203721"},"Children":[{"ID":"20220906203722-wh9e2bt","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20220906203722-wh9e2bt","updated":"20220906203722"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"都是基于内存的数据库，一般都用来当做缓存使用。","Properties":{"id":""}}]}]},{"ID":"20220906203723-lp6qmhu","Type":"NodeListItem","Data":"2","ListData":{"Typ":1,"Tight":true,"Start":2,"Delimiter":46,"Padding":3,"Marker":"Mg==","Num":2},"Properties":{"id":"20220906203723-lp6qmhu","updated":"20220906203723"},"Children":[{"ID":"20220906203724-n50vect","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20220906203724-n50vect","updated":"20220906203724"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"都有过期策略。","Properties":{"id":""}}]}]},{"ID":"20220906203725-cp7ow8k","Type":"NodeListItem","Data":"3","ListData":{"Typ":1,"Tight":true,"Start":3,"Delimiter":46,"Padding":3,"Marker":"Mw==","Num":3},"Properties":{"id":"20220906203725-cp7ow8k","updated":"20220906203725"},"Children":[{"ID":"20220906203726-ca26rcg","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20220906203726-ca26rcg","updated":"20220906203726"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"两者的性能都非常高。","Properties":{"id":""}}]}]}]},{"ID":"20220906203727-op3nhb7","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20220906203727-op3nhb7","updated":"20220906203727"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","Properties":{"id":""},"TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"区别"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":" ：","Properties":{"id":""}}]},{"ID":"20220906203728-gc8fg3o","Type":"NodeList","ListData":{"Typ":1,"Tight":true,"Start":1,"Delimiter":46,"Padding":3,"Marker":"MQ==","Num":1},"Properties":{"id":"20220906203728-gc8fg3o","updated":"20220906203728"},"Children":[{"ID":"20220906203729-c49p2u0","Type":"NodeListItem","Data":"1","ListData":{"Typ":1,"Tight":true,"Start":1,"Delimiter":46,"Padding":3,"Marker":"MQ==","Num":1},"Properties":{"id":"20220906203729-c49p2u0","updated":"20220906203729"},"Children":[{"ID":"20220906203730-s5771gt","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20220906203730-s5771gt","updated":"20220906203730"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","Properties":{"id":""},"TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"Redis 支持更丰富的数据类型（支持更复杂的应用场景）"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"。Redis 不仅仅支持简单的 k/v 类型的数据，同时还提供 list，set，zset，hash 等数据结构的存储。Memcached 只支持最简单的 k/v 数据类型。","Properties":{"id":""}}]}]},{"ID":"20220906203731-0a7a7rd","Type":"NodeListItem","Data":"2","ListData":{"Typ":1,"Tight":true,"Start":2,"Delimiter":46,"Padding":3,"Marker":"Mg==","Num":2},"Properties":{"id":"20220906203731-0a7a7rd","updated":"20220906203731"},"Children":[{"ID":"20220906203732-jltzzgx","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20220906203732-jltzzgx","updated":"20220906203732"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","Properties":{"id":""},"TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"Redis 支持数据的持久化，可以将内存中的数据保持在磁盘中，重启的时候可以再次加载进行使用,而 Memcached 把数据全部存在内存之中。"}]}]},{"ID":"20220906203733-nxwbgpd","Type":"NodeListItem","Data":"3","ListData":{"Typ":1,"Tight":true,"Start":3,"Delimiter":46,"Padding":3,"Marker":"Mw==","Num":3},"Properties":{"id":"20220906203733-nxwbgpd","updated":"20220906203733"},"Children":[{"ID":"20220906203734-ybviih1","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20220906203734-ybviih1","updated":"20220906203734"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","Properties":{"id":""},"TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"Redis 有灾难恢复机制。"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":" 因为可以把缓存中的数据持久化到磁盘上。","Properties":{"id":""}}]}]},{"ID":"20220906203735-3oj21ff","Type":"NodeListItem","Data":"4","ListData":{"Typ":1,"Tight":true,"Start":4,"Delimiter":46,"Padding":3,"Marker":"NA==","Num":4},"Properties":{"id":"20220906203735-3oj21ff","updated":"20220906203735"},"Children":[{"ID":"20220906203736-ok9ec5x","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20220906203736-ok9ec5x","updated":"20220906203736"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","Properties":{"id":""},"TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"Redis 在服务器内存使用完之后，可以将不用的数据放到磁盘上。但是，Memcached 在服务器内存使用完之后，就会直接报异常。"}]}]},{"ID":"20220906203737-fops96w","Type":"NodeListItem","Data":"5","ListData":{"Typ":1,"Tight":true,"Start":5,"Delimiter":46,"Padding":3,"Marker":"NQ==","Num":5},"Properties":{"id":"20220906203737-fops96w","updated":"20220906203737"},"Children":[{"ID":"20220906203738-aitogcc","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20220906203738-aitogcc","updated":"20220906203738"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","Properties":{"id":""},"TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"Memcached 没有原生的集群模式，需要依靠客户端来实现往集群中分片写入数据；但是 Redis 目前是原生支持 cluster 模式的。"}]}]},{"ID":"20220906203739-knculte","Type":"NodeListItem","Data":"6","ListData":{"Typ":1,"Tight":true,"Start":6,"Delimiter":46,"Padding":3,"Marker":"Ng==","Num":6},"Properties":{"id":"20220906203739-knculte","updated":"20220906203739"},"Children":[{"ID":"20220906203740-v7shrlh","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20220906203740-v7shrlh","updated":"20220906203740"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","Properties":{"id":""},"TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"Memcached 是多线程，非阻塞 IO 复用的网络模型；Redis 使用单线程的多路 IO 复用模型。"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":" （Redis 6.0 引入了多线程 IO ）","Properties":{"id":""}}]}]},{"ID":"20220906203741-nnbsb9r","Type":"NodeListItem","Data":"7","ListData":{"Typ":1,"Tight":true,"Start":7,"Delimiter":46,"Padding":3,"Marker":"Nw==","Num":7},"Properties":{"id":"20220906203741-nnbsb9r","updated":"20220906203741"},"Children":[{"ID":"20220906203742-0rhhl85","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20220906203742-0rhhl85","updated":"20220906203742"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","Properties":{"id":""},"TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"Redis 支持发布订阅模型、Lua 脚本、事务等功能，而 Memcached 不支持。并且，Redis 支持更多的编程语言。"}]}]},{"ID":"20220906203743-qvvf5lq","Type":"NodeListItem","Data":"8","ListData":{"Typ":1,"Tight":true,"Start":8,"Delimiter":46,"Padding":3,"Marker":"OA==","Num":8},"Properties":{"id":"20220906203743-qvvf5lq","updated":"20220906203743"},"Children":[{"ID":"20220906203744-9rra1k0","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20220906203744-9rra1k0","updated":"20220906203744"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","Properties":{"id":""},"TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"Memcached 过期数据的删除策略只用了惰性删除，而 Redis 同时使用了惰性删除与定期删除。"}]}]}]},{"ID":"20220906203745-gmxazko","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20220906203745-gmxazko","updated":"20220906203745"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"相信看了上面的对比之后，我们已经没有什么理由可以选择使用 Memcached 来作为自己项目的分布式缓存了。","Properties":{"id":""}}]},{"ID":"20220906203746-ecn6wvp","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":4,"Properties":{"id":"20220906203746-ecn6wvp","updated":"20220906203746"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeHeadingC8hMarker","Data":"#### ","Properties":{"id":""}},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"缓存数据的处理流程是怎样的？","Properties":{"id":""}}]},{"ID":"20220906203747-c3gjswr","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20220906203747-c3gjswr","updated":"20220906203747"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"作为暖男一号，我给大家画了一个草图。","Properties":{"id":""}}]},{"ID":"20220906203748-28uz7pi","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20220906203748-28uz7pi","updated":"20220906203748"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeImage","Properties":{"id":""},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeBang","Data":"!","Properties":{"id":""}},{"Type":"NodeOpenBracket","Data":"[","Properties":{"id":""}},{"Type":"NodeLinkText","Data":"正常缓存处理流程","Properties":{"id":""}},{"Type":"NodeCloseBracket","Data":"]","Properties":{"id":""}},{"Type":"NodeOpenParen","Data":"(","Properties":{"id":""}},{"Type":"NodeLinkDest","Data":"https://guide-blog-images.oss-cn-shenzhen.aliyuncs.com/github/javaguide/database/redis/normal-cache-process.png","Properties":{"id":""}},{"Type":"NodeCloseParen","Data":")","Properties":{"id":""}}]}]},{"ID":"20220906203749-jptxxcw","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20220906203749-jptxxcw","updated":"20220906203749"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"简单来说就是:","Properties":{"id":""}}]},{"ID":"20220906203750-bukmtvu","Type":"NodeList","ListData":{"Typ":1,"Tight":true,"Start":1,"Delimiter":46,"Padding":3,"Marker":"MQ==","Num":1},"Properties":{"id":"20220906203750-bukmtvu","updated":"20220906203750"},"Children":[{"ID":"20220906203751-rxszjld","Type":"NodeListItem","Data":"1","ListData":{"Typ":1,"Tight":true,"Start":1,"Delimiter":46,"Padding":3,"Marker":"MQ==","Num":1},"Properties":{"id":"20220906203751-rxszjld","updated":"20220906203751"},"Children":[{"ID":"20220906203752-3ik3q79","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20220906203752-3ik3q79","updated":"20220906203752"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"如果用户请求的数据在缓存中就直接返回。","Properties":{"id":""}}]}]},{"ID":"20220906203753-0floq4q","Type":"NodeListItem","Data":"2","ListData":{"Typ":1,"Tight":true,"Start":2,"Delimiter":46,"Padding":3,"Marker":"Mg==","Num":2},"Properties":{"id":"20220906203753-0floq4q","updated":"20220906203753"},"Children":[{"ID":"20220906203754-oukwubk","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20220906203754-oukwubk","updated":"20220906203754"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"缓存中不存在的话就看数据库中是否存在。","Properties":{"id":""}}]}]},{"ID":"20220906203755-8mf2h1v","Type":"NodeListItem","Data":"3","ListData":{"Typ":1,"Tight":true,"Start":3,"Delimiter":46,"Padding":3,"Marker":"Mw==","Num":3},"Properties":{"id":"20220906203755-8mf2h1v","updated":"20220906203755"},"Children":[{"ID":"20220906203756-ph4x9ps","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20220906203756-ph4x9ps","updated":"20220906203756"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"数据库中存在的话就更新缓存中的数据。","Properties":{"id":""}}]}]},{"ID":"20220906203757-untngij","Type":"NodeListItem","Data":"4","ListData":{"Typ":1,"Tight":true,"Start":4,"Delimiter":46,"Padding":3,"Marker":"NA==","Num":4},"Properties":{"id":"20220906203757-untngij","updated":"20220906203757"},"Children":[{"ID":"20220906203758-nirsqpr","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20220906203758-nirsqpr","updated":"20220906203758"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"数据库中不存在的话就返回空数据。","Properties":{"id":""}}]}]}]},{"ID":"20220906203759-hf089os","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":4,"Properties":{"id":"20220906203759-hf089os","updated":"20220906203759"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeHeadingC8hMarker","Data":"#### ","Properties":{"id":""}},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"为什么要用 Redis/为什么要用缓存？","Properties":{"id":""}}]},{"ID":"20220906203760-p8civf2","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20220906203760-p8civf2","updated":"20220906203760"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","Properties":{"id":""},"TextMarkType":"em","TextMarkTextContent":"简单，来说使用缓存主要是为了提升用户体验以及应对更多的用户。"}]},{"ID":"20220906203761-siedj2k","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20220906203761-siedj2k","updated":"20220906203761"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"下面我们主要从“高性能”和“高并发”这两点来看待这个问题。","Properties":{"id":""}}]},{"ID":"20220906203762-ywz3py8","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20220906203762-ywz3py8","updated":"20220906203762"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeImage","Properties":{"id":""},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeBang","Data":"!","Properties":{"id":""}},{"Type":"NodeOpenBracket","Data":"[","Properties":{"id":""}},{"Type":"NodeLinkText","Data":"使用缓存之后","Properties":{"id":""}},{"Type":"NodeCloseBracket","Data":"]","Properties":{"id":""}},{"Type":"NodeOpenParen","Data":"(","Properties":{"id":""}},{"Type":"NodeLinkDest","Data":"https://guide-blog-images.oss-cn-shenzhen.aliyuncs.com/github/javaguide/database/redis/after-using-the-cache.png","Properties":{"id":""}},{"Type":"NodeCloseParen","Data":")","Properties":{"id":""}}]}]},{"ID":"20220906203763-4fcjn5h","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20220906203763-4fcjn5h","updated":"20220906203763"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","Properties":{"id":""},"TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"高性能"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":" ：","Properties":{"id":""}}]},{"ID":"20220906203764-i6pb9wk","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20220906203764-i6pb9wk","updated":"20220906203764"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"对照上面 👆 我画的图。我们设想这样的场景：","Properties":{"id":""}}]},{"ID":"20220906203765-j1qdmg3","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20220906203765-j1qdmg3","updated":"20220906203765"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"假如用户第一次访问数据库中的某些数据的话，这个过程是比较慢，毕竟是从硬盘中读取的。但是，如果说，用户访问的数据属于高频数据并且不会经常改变的话，那么我们就可以很放心地将该用户访问的数据存在缓存中。","Properties":{"id":""}}]},{"ID":"20220906203766-mqgls6l","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20220906203766-mqgls6l","updated":"20220906203766"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","Properties":{"id":""},"TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"这样有什么好处呢？"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":" 那就是保证用户下一次再访问这些数据的时候就可以直接从缓存中获取了。操作缓存就是直接操作内存，所以速度相当快。","Properties":{"id":""}}]},{"ID":"20220906203767-meb9lti","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20220906203767-meb9lti","updated":"20220906203767"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"不过，要保持数据库和缓存中的数据的一致性。 如果数据库中的对应数据改变的之后，同步改变缓存中相应的数据即可！","Properties":{"id":""}}]},{"ID":"20220906203768-1ta8jgz","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20220906203768-1ta8jgz","updated":"20220906203768"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","Properties":{"id":""},"TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"高并发："}]},{"ID":"20220906203769-zah8qth","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20220906203769-zah8qth","updated":"20220906203769"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"一般像 MySQL 这类的数据库的 QPS 大概都在 1w 左右（4 核 8g） ，但是使用 Redis 缓存之后很容易达到 10w+，甚至最高能达到 30w+（就单机 redis 的情况，redis 集群的话会更高）。","Properties":{"id":""}}]},{"ID":"20220906203770-s1thzy5","Type":"NodeBlockquote","Properties":{"id":"20220906203770-s1thzy5","updated":"20220906203770"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeBlockquoteMarker","Data":"\u003e ","Properties":{"id":""}},{"ID":"20220906203771-9zrsrmu","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20220906203771-9zrsrmu","updated":"20220906203771"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"QPS（Query Per Second）：服务器每秒可以执行的查询次数；","Properties":{"id":""}}]}]},{"ID":"20220906203772-r0ewibf","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20220906203772-r0ewibf","updated":"20220906203772"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"由此可见，直接操作缓存能够承受的数据库请求数量是远远大于直接访问数据库的，所以我们可以考虑把数据库中的部分数据转移到缓存中去，这样用户的一部分请求会直接到缓存这里而不用经过数据库。进而，我们也就提高了系统整体的并发。","Properties":{"id":""}}]},{"ID":"20220906203773-r8xp8mz","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":4,"Properties":{"id":"20220906203773-r8xp8mz","updated":"20220906203773"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeHeadingC8hMarker","Data":"#### ","Properties":{"id":""}},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"Redis 除了做缓存，还能做什么？","Properties":{"id":""}}]},{"ID":"20220906203774-edwtd14","Type":"NodeList","ListData":{"Tight":true,"BulletChar":45,"Padding":2,"Marker":"LQ==","Num":-1},"Properties":{"id":"20220906203774-edwtd14","updated":"20220906203774"},"Children":[{"ID":"20220906203775-gmdope0","Type":"NodeListItem","Data":"-","ListData":{"Tight":true,"BulletChar":45,"Padding":2,"Marker":"LQ==","Num":-1},"Properties":{"id":"20220906203775-gmdope0","updated":"20220906203775"},"Children":[{"ID":"20220906203776-950deun","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20220906203776-950deun","updated":"20220906203776"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","Properties":{"id":""},"TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"分布式锁"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":" ： 通过 Redis 来做分布式锁是一种比较常见的方式。通常情况下，我们都是基于 Redisson 来实现分布式锁。相关阅读：","Properties":{"id":""}},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","Properties":{"id":""},"TextMarkType":"a","TextMarkAHref":"https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s/CbnPRfvq4m1sqo2uKI6qQw","TextMarkTextContent":"《分布式锁中的王者方案 - Redisson》"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"。","Properties":{"id":""}}]}]},{"ID":"20220906203777-2kmo5tp","Type":"NodeListItem","Data":"-","ListData":{"Tight":true,"BulletChar":45,"Padding":2,"Marker":"LQ==","Num":-1},"Properties":{"id":"20220906203777-2kmo5tp","updated":"20220906203777"},"Children":[{"ID":"20220906203778-ctw8vvu","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20220906203778-ctw8vvu","updated":"20220906203778"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","Properties":{"id":""},"TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"限流"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":" ：一般是通过 Redis + Lua 脚本的方式来实现限流。相关阅读：","Properties":{"id":""}},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","Properties":{"id":""},"TextMarkType":"a","TextMarkAHref":"https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s/kyFAWH3mVNJvurQDt4vchA","TextMarkTextContent":"《我司用了 6 年的 Redis 分布式限流器，可以说是非常厉害了！》"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"。","Properties":{"id":""}}]}]},{"ID":"20220906203779-trsvluj","Type":"NodeListItem","Data":"-","ListData":{"Tight":true,"BulletChar":45,"Padding":2,"Marker":"LQ==","Num":-1},"Properties":{"id":"20220906203779-trsvluj","updated":"20220906203779"},"Children":[{"ID":"20220906203780-um2hh1c","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20220906203780-um2hh1c","updated":"20220906203780"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","Properties":{"id":""},"TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"消息队列"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":" ：Redis 自带的 list 数据结构可以作为一个简单的队列使用。Redis 5.0 中增加的 Stream 类型的数据结构更加适合用来做消息队列。它比较类似于 Kafka，有主题和消费组的概念，支持消息持久化以及 ACK 机制。","Properties":{"id":""}}]}]},{"ID":"20220906203781-ipvygdr","Type":"NodeListItem","Data":"-","ListData":{"Tight":true,"BulletChar":45,"Padding":2,"Marker":"LQ==","Num":-1},"Properties":{"id":"20220906203781-ipvygdr","updated":"20220906203781"},"Children":[{"ID":"20220906203782-yjivzuq","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20220906203782-yjivzuq","updated":"20220906203782"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","Properties":{"id":""},"TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"复杂业务场景"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":" ：通过 Redis 以及 Redis 扩展（比如 Redisson）提供的数据结构，我们可以很方便地完成很多复杂的业务场景比如通过 bitmap 统计活跃用户、通过 sorted set 维护排行榜。","Properties":{"id":""}}]}]},{"ID":"20220906203783-odqxfgg","Type":"NodeListItem","Data":"-","ListData":{"Tight":true,"BulletChar":45,"Padding":2,"Marker":"LQ==","Num":-1},"Properties":{"id":"20220906203783-odqxfgg","updated":"20220906203783"},"Children":[{"ID":"20220906203784-2bz0dr4","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20220906203784-2bz0dr4","updated":"20220906203784"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"......","Properties":{"id":""}}]}]}]},{"ID":"20220906203785-rgahsa8","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":4,"Properties":{"id":"20220906203785-rgahsa8","updated":"20220906203785"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeHeadingC8hMarker","Data":"#### ","Properties":{"id":""}},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"Redis 可以做消息队列么？","Properties":{"id":""}}]},{"ID":"20220906203786-fgou849","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20220906203786-fgou849","updated":"20220906203786"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"Redis 5.0 新增加的一个数据结构 ","Properties":{"id":""}},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","Properties":{"id":""},"TextMarkType":"code","TextMarkTextContent":"Stream"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":" 可以用来做消息队列，","Properties":{"id":""}},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","Properties":{"id":""},"TextMarkType":"code","TextMarkTextContent":"Stream"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":" 支持：","Properties":{"id":""}}]},{"ID":"20220906203787-l5tjapw","Type":"NodeList","ListData":{"Tight":true,"BulletChar":45,"Padding":2,"Marker":"LQ==","Num":-1},"Properties":{"id":"20220906203787-l5tjapw","updated":"20220906203787"},"Children":[{"ID":"20220906203788-6ckudiw","Type":"NodeListItem","Data":"-","ListData":{"Tight":true,"BulletChar":45,"Padding":2,"Marker":"LQ==","Num":-1},"Properties":{"id":"20220906203788-6ckudiw","updated":"20220906203788"},"Children":[{"ID":"20220906203789-n7xnvtl","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20220906203789-n7xnvtl","updated":"20220906203789"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"发布 / 订阅模式","Properties":{"id":""}}]}]},{"ID":"20220906203790-zi4pf4u","Type":"NodeListItem","Data":"-","ListData":{"Tight":true,"BulletChar":45,"Padding":2,"Marker":"LQ==","Num":-1},"Properties":{"id":"20220906203790-zi4pf4u","updated":"20220906203790"},"Children":[{"ID":"20220906203791-ay7wmln","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20220906203791-ay7wmln","updated":"20220906203791"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"按照消费者组进行消费","Properties":{"id":""}}]}]},{"ID":"20220906203792-n2gd5kd","Type":"NodeListItem","Data":"-","ListData":{"Tight":true,"BulletChar":45,"Padding":2,"Marker":"LQ==","Num":-1},"Properties":{"id":"20220906203792-n2gd5kd","updated":"20220906203792"},"Children":[{"ID":"20220906203793-j9t1re0","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20220906203793-j9t1re0","updated":"20220906203793"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"消息持久化（ RDB 和 AOF）","Properties":{"id":""}}]}]}]},{"ID":"20220906203794-o7mcqti","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20220906203794-o7mcqti","updated":"20220906203794"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"不过，和专业的消息队列相比，还是有很多欠缺的地方比如消息丢失和堆积问题不好解决。因此，我们通常建议是不使用 Redis 来做消息队列的，你完全可以选择市面上比较成熟的一些消息队列比如 RocketMQ、Kafka。","Properties":{"id":""}}]},{"ID":"20220906203795-ar4lps5","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20220906203795-ar4lps5","updated":"20220906203795"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"相关文章推荐：","Properties":{"id":""}},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","Properties":{"id":""},"TextMarkType":"a","TextMarkAHref":"https://javakeeper.starfish.ink/data-management/Redis/Redis-MQ.html","TextMarkTextContent":"Redis 消息队列的三种方案（List、Streams、Pub/Sub）"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"。","Properties":{"id":""}}]},{"ID":"20220906203796-5f7dcpi","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":3,"Properties":{"id":"20220906203796-5f7dcpi","updated":"20220906203796"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeHeadingC8hMarker","Data":"### ","Properties":{"id":""}},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"Redis 数据结构","Properties":{"id":""}}]},{"ID":"20220906203797-grbf2aq","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":4,"Properties":{"id":"20220906203797-grbf2aq","updated":"20220906203797"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeHeadingC8hMarker","Data":"#### ","Properties":{"id":""}},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"Redis 常用的数据结构有哪些？","Properties":{"id":""}}]},{"ID":"20220906203798-o6bwvqt","Type":"NodeList","ListData":{"Tight":true,"BulletChar":45,"Padding":2,"Marker":"LQ==","Num":-1},"Properties":{"id":"20220906203798-o6bwvqt","updated":"20220906203798"},"Children":[{"ID":"20220906203799-38prqag","Type":"NodeListItem","Data":"-","ListData":{"Tight":true,"BulletChar":45,"Padding":2,"Marker":"LQ==","Num":-1},"Properties":{"id":"20220906203799-38prqag","updated":"20220906203799"},"Children":[{"ID":"20220906203800-hhx891v","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20220906203800-hhx891v","updated":"20220906203800"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","Properties":{"id":""},"TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"5 种基础数据结构"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":" ：String（字符串）、List（列表）、Set（集合）、Hash（散列）、Zset（有序集合）。","Properties":{"id":""}}]}]},{"ID":"20220906203801-u54x5f2","Type":"NodeListItem","Data":"-","ListData":{"Tight":true,"BulletChar":45,"Padding":2,"Marker":"LQ==","Num":-1},"Properties":{"id":"20220906203801-u54x5f2","updated":"20220906203801"},"Children":[{"ID":"20220906203802-7su6uga","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20220906203802-7su6uga","updated":"20220906203802"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","Properties":{"id":""},"TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"3 种特殊数据结构"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":" ：HyperLogLogs（基数统计）、Bitmap （位存储）、Geospatial (地理位置)。","Properties":{"id":""}}]}]}]},{"ID":"20220906203803-h8ftetp","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20220906203803-h8ftetp","updated":"20220906203803"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"关于 5 种基础数据结构的详细介绍请看这篇文章：","Properties":{"id":""}},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","Properties":{"id":""},"TextMarkType":"a","TextMarkAHref":"https://javaguide.cn/database/redis/redis-data-structures-01.html","TextMarkTextContent":"Redis 5 种基本数据结构详解"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"。","Properties":{"id":""}}]},{"ID":"20220906203804-co5nwdl","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20220906203804-co5nwdl","updated":"20220906203804"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"关于 3 种特殊数据结构的详细介绍请看这篇文章：","Properties":{"id":""}},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","Properties":{"id":""},"TextMarkType":"a","TextMarkAHref":"https://javaguide.cn/database/redis/redis-data-structures-02.html","TextMarkTextContent":"Redis 3 种特殊数据结构详解"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"。","Properties":{"id":""}}]},{"ID":"20220906203805-l8bkyph","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":4,"Properties":{"id":"20220906203805-l8bkyph","updated":"20220906203805"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeHeadingC8hMarker","Data":"#### ","Properties":{"id":""}},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"String 的应用场景有哪些？","Properties":{"id":""}}]},{"ID":"20220906203806-fpzjcjp","Type":"NodeList","ListData":{"Tight":true,"BulletChar":45,"Padding":2,"Marker":"LQ==","Num":-1},"Properties":{"id":"20220906203806-fpzjcjp","updated":"20220906203806"},"Children":[{"ID":"20220906203807-ofx1nxq","Type":"NodeListItem","Data":"-","ListData":{"Tight":true,"BulletChar":45,"Padding":2,"Marker":"LQ==","Num":-1},"Properties":{"id":"20220906203807-ofx1nxq","updated":"20220906203807"},"Children":[{"ID":"20220906203808-x3i0cvp","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20220906203808-x3i0cvp","updated":"20220906203808"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"常规数据（比如 session、token、、序列化后的对象）的缓存；","Properties":{"id":""}}]}]},{"ID":"20220906203809-rl1zj9k","Type":"NodeListItem","Data":"-","ListData":{"Tight":true,"BulletChar":45,"Padding":2,"Marker":"LQ==","Num":-1},"Properties":{"id":"20220906203809-rl1zj9k","updated":"20220906203809"},"Children":[{"ID":"20220906203810-lv4fb0p","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20220906203810-lv4fb0p","updated":"20220906203810"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"计数比如用户单位时间的请求数（简单限流可以用到）、页面单位时间的访问数；","Properties":{"id":""}}]}]},{"ID":"20220906203811-ymyy1da","Type":"NodeListItem","Data":"-","ListData":{"Tight":true,"BulletChar":45,"Padding":2,"Marker":"LQ==","Num":-1},"Properties":{"id":"20220906203811-ymyy1da","updated":"20220906203811"},"Children":[{"ID":"20220906203812-onjni5g","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20220906203812-onjni5g","updated":"20220906203812"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"分布式锁(利用 ","Properties":{"id":""}},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","Properties":{"id":""},"TextMarkType":"code","TextMarkTextContent":"SETNX key value"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":" 命令可以实现一个最简易的分布式锁)；","Properties":{"id":""}}]}]},{"ID":"20220906203813-nqtckwz","Type":"NodeListItem","Data":"-","ListData":{"Tight":true,"BulletChar":45,"Padding":2,"Marker":"LQ==","Num":-1},"Properties":{"id":"20220906203813-nqtckwz","updated":"20220906203813"},"Children":[{"ID":"20220906203814-ag05mkj","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20220906203814-ag05mkj","updated":"20220906203814"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"......","Properties":{"id":""}}]}]}]},{"ID":"20220906203815-8qmn8xh","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20220906203815-8qmn8xh","updated":"20220906203815"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"关于 String 的详细介绍请看这篇文章：","Properties":{"id":""}},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","Properties":{"id":""},"TextMarkType":"a","TextMarkAHref":"https://javaguide.cn/database/redis/redis-data-structures-01.html","TextMarkTextContent":"Redis 5 种基本数据结构详解"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"。","Properties":{"id":""}}]},{"ID":"20220906203816-10fpwbl","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":4,"Properties":{"id":"20220906203816-10fpwbl","updated":"20220906203816"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeHeadingC8hMarker","Data":"#### ","Properties":{"id":""}},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"String 还是 Hash 存储对象数据更好呢？","Properties":{"id":""}}]},{"ID":"20220906203817-p7nve2b","Type":"NodeList","ListData":{"Tight":true,"BulletChar":45,"Padding":2,"Marker":"LQ==","Num":-1},"Properties":{"id":"20220906203817-p7nve2b","updated":"20220906203817"},"Children":[{"ID":"20220906203818-675tpku","Type":"NodeListItem","Data":"-","ListData":{"Tight":true,"BulletChar":45,"Padding":2,"Marker":"LQ==","Num":-1},"Properties":{"id":"20220906203818-675tpku","updated":"20220906203818"},"Children":[{"ID":"20220906203819-es7o4uz","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20220906203819-es7o4uz","updated":"20220906203819"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"String 存储的是序列化后的对象数据，存放的是整个对象。Hash 是对对象的每个字段单独存储，可以获取部分字段的信息，也可以修改或者添加部分字段，节省网络流量。如果对象中某些字段需要经常变动或者经常需要单独查询对象中的个别字段信息，Hash 就非常适合。","Properties":{"id":""}}]}]},{"ID":"20220906203820-571tz1t","Type":"NodeListItem","Data":"-","ListData":{"Tight":true,"BulletChar":45,"Padding":2,"Marker":"LQ==","Num":-1},"Properties":{"id":"20220906203820-571tz1t","updated":"20220906203820"},"Children":[{"ID":"20220906203821-zs62qok","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20220906203821-zs62qok","updated":"20220906203821"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"String 存储相对来说更加节省内存，缓存相同数量的对象数据，String 消耗的内存约是 Hash 的一半。并且，存储具有多层嵌套的对象时也方便很多。如果系统对性能和资源消耗非常敏感的话，String 就非常适合。","Properties":{"id":""}}]}]}]},{"ID":"20220906203822-e5i30bq","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20220906203822-e5i30bq","updated":"20220906203822"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"在绝大部分情况，我们建议使用 String 来存储对象数据即可！","Properties":{"id":""}}]},{"ID":"20220906203823-2fhc0di","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20220906203823-2fhc0di","updated":"20220906203823"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"那根据你的介绍，购物车信息用 String 还是 Hash 存储更好呢?","Properties":{"id":""}}]},{"ID":"20220906203824-7eptebg","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20220906203824-7eptebg","updated":"20220906203824"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"购物车信息建议使用 Hash 存储：","Properties":{"id":""}}]},{"ID":"20220906203825-ybawrv3","Type":"NodeList","ListData":{"Tight":true,"BulletChar":45,"Padding":2,"Marker":"LQ==","Num":-1},"Properties":{"id":"20220906203825-ybawrv3","updated":"20220906203825"},"Children":[{"ID":"20220906203826-3pl3uqt","Type":"NodeListItem","Data":"-","ListData":{"Tight":true,"BulletChar":45,"Padding":2,"Marker":"LQ==","Num":-1},"Properties":{"id":"20220906203826-3pl3uqt","updated":"20220906203826"},"Children":[{"ID":"20220906203827-oji61c9","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20220906203827-oji61c9","updated":"20220906203827"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"用户 id 为 key","Properties":{"id":""}}]}]},{"ID":"20220906203828-55yms03","Type":"NodeListItem","Data":"-","ListData":{"Tight":true,"BulletChar":45,"Padding":2,"Marker":"LQ==","Num":-1},"Properties":{"id":"20220906203828-55yms03","updated":"20220906203828"},"Children":[{"ID":"20220906203829-mqgna1f","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20220906203829-mqgna1f","updated":"20220906203829"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"商品 id 为 field，商品数量为 value","Properties":{"id":""}}]}]}]},{"ID":"20220906203830-wjj7i0k","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20220906203830-wjj7i0k","updated":"20220906203830"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"由于购物车中的商品频繁修改和变动，这个时候 Hash 就非常适合了！","Properties":{"id":""}}]},{"ID":"20220906203831-k2nnwq6","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":4,"Properties":{"id":"20220906203831-k2nnwq6","updated":"20220906203831"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeHeadingC8hMarker","Data":"#### ","Properties":{"id":""}},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"使用 Redis 实现一个排行榜怎么做？","Properties":{"id":""}}]},{"ID":"20220906203832-7ays6ji","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20220906203832-7ays6ji","updated":"20220906203832"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"Redis 中有一个叫做 ","Properties":{"id":""}},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","Properties":{"id":""},"TextMarkType":"code","TextMarkTextContent":"sorted set"},{"T